OC LIGHT already has a Language Translator/Editor built-in, and with a 
tool like linked below, it's possible to complete still missing Parts 
in other OC 1.5.6.x based Releases. Onby a range of links, the first 
link contains MaxD's original OpenShop 1.5.6.1 Languages:
http://www.ipc.li/os/Openshop_languages.zip
and here are some nice free OC v.1.5.6.x Admin Language Editors:
http://www.ipc.li/os/LanguageEditor.zip
http://www.ipc.li/os/magic-translations.zip
http://www.ipc.li/os/LanguageEditor_oc_v_1_5_6_x.zip
other Language related Files:
https://github.com/IP-CAM/OpenCartTranslator
https://github.com/IP-CAM/Opencart-simple-translate
https://www.opencart.com/index.php?route=marketplace/extension&filter_search=arabic
https://www.opencart.com/index.php?route=marketplace/extension/info&extension_id=29
https://www.opencart.com/index.php?route=marketplace/extension/info&extension_id=34134
https://www.opencart.com/index.php?route=marketplace/extension/info&extension_id=24295
http://translate.opencart.com/
I also added a range of languages to my repositories.
